    <strong>Triple Whale starts at $129/month</strong> (Starter, annual billing). The Growth plan is $299/month and the Pro plan is $599/month. Monthly billing adds approximately 20% to each tier. There is no permanent free plan — only a 7-day free trial.
  </p>

