  <h2>// Is Triple Whale Worth the Cost?</h2>
  <p>
    Triple Whale is designed for Shopify stores running significant paid advertising budgets — typically $10,000/month or more on Meta and Google combined. At that spend level, improving attribution accuracy by even 10–15% can represent tens of thousands of dollars in better-allocated ad budget, making $129–$299/month relatively low cost-per-insight.
  </p>
  <p>
    For stores under $50,000/month in revenue or under $5,000/month in ad spend, the ROI case is harder to make. Shopify's native analytics, combined with free server-side tracking tools, often covers what early-stage stores actually need to make sound media buying decisions.
  </p>

