    <p style="margin:0; font-size:13px;">Stack Architect's <a href="/shopify-profit-loss-automation">Shopify P&L Automation</a> delivers live profit and loss tracking in Google Sheets — covering revenue, COGS, app costs, and ad spend — at zero cost. For stores not yet at the scale where Triple Whale's attribution layer pays for itself, this covers the core reporting needs.</p>
  </div>

  <!-- FAQ ACCORDION -->
  <div class="faq-section">
    <h2>// Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <button class="faq-question">Does Triple Whale offer a free trial?<span class="chevron">▾</span></button>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        Yes. Triple Whale offers a 7-day free trial with access to Growth plan features. No permanent free plan is available — after the trial expires, a paid subscription starting at $129/month (annual) is required to continue.
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <button class="faq-question">Can I cancel Triple Whale at any time?<span class="chevron">▾</span></button>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        On monthly billing, you can cancel at any time with no penalty. On annual billing, Triple Whale's standard terms do not offer mid-year refunds — you are committed to the full annual contract. Read the cancellation terms before committing to an annual plan.
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <button class="faq-question">Does Triple Whale pricing scale with store revenue?<span class="chevron">▾</span></button>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        Triple Whale's listed pricing is flat per tier and does not scale with revenue or order volume. However, enterprise pricing for high-volume stores is negotiated separately. Triple Whale may also charge differently for stores exceeding certain data thresholds — confirm with their sales team if you process more than 50,000 orders per month.
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <button class="faq-question">What ad channels does Triple Whale support?<span class="chevron">▾</span></button>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        Triple Whale supports Meta Ads (Facebook and Instagram), Google Ads, TikTok Ads, Snapchat Ads, Pinterest Ads, and Klaviyo email attribution. All major paid channels used by Shopify merchants are covered. Organic attribution via UTM parameters is also supported.
      </div>
    </div>
